This is a 3-PART SERIES. Each part is a separate video. Viewers must follow to see the next part.

Requirements:
1. hook_text: A Reddit post title summarizing the FULL story. 10-20 words. Focus on BETRAYAL and REVENGE. Examples:
   - "My best friend slept with my fiance so I ruined both their careers"
   - "My boss stole my promotion so I got him fired and took his job"
   - "I caught my sister stealing from our dying mother's bank account"

2. parts: An array of exactly 3 objects, each representing one video part:

   Part 1 — THE BETRAYAL (120-150 words):
   - Set the scene: who are the people, what was the relationship
   - Build trust, show normalcy, then DROP the betrayal
   - End on a HARD CLIFFHANGER: "And that's when I saw the texts..." or "But what I found next destroyed everything..."
   - Last line MUST be: "Follow for Part 2."

   Part 2 — THE PLAN (120-150 words):
   - Brief 1-sentence recap of Part 1
   - The situation escalates — more betrayal discovered, or the revenge plan takes shape
   - Show the protagonist preparing, gathering evidence, making moves
   - End on cliffhanger: "Everything was in place. All I had to do was make one call..." or "And then... I pressed send."
   - Last line MUST be: "Follow for Part 3 — the finale."

   Part 3 — THE PAYOFF (120-150 words):
   - Brief recap, then deliver the FULL revenge/justice
   - Show the consequences: what happened to the betrayer
   - Include aftermath and fallout
   - End with verdict: "Was I wrong? Comment below." or "Would you have done the same?"
   - This is the finale — no "follow for part X."

   Each part object must have:
   - "voiceover_script": Narration for this part (120-150 words STRICT)
   - "part_label": "Part 1", "Part 2", or "Part 3"
   - "part_hook": 5-10 word SPECIFIC teaser for screen overlay. MUST reference a concrete detail, NOT be vague.
     GOOD: "The FBI found $2M in his basement" / "She recorded every conversation for 6 months" / "His own lawyer testified against him"
     BAD: "The plan unfolds" / "Empire crumbles" / "Justice served" (too generic, no story detail)

3. narrator_gender: "male" or "female" — based on the protagonist's gender. Look at pronouns and context.

4. subreddit: Best fitting subreddit (NuclearRevenge, ProRevenge, pettyrevenge, BestofRedditorUpdates)
5. captions: Per-platform captions with "Part X/3" included.
6. hashtags: Array of 10 hashtags including {{ niche.hashtags[:5] | join(', ') }}
7. thumbnail_prompt: Dramatic scene from the story.

8. music_tags: ["lofi", "ambient", "chill", "soft"] — subtle lo-fi background only.
9. music_speed: "low" — casual background atmosphere.

